            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <p>
                        Copyright &copy; 2021 Kromel Makina A.Ş.

                        - Design: <a rel="nofollow noopener" href="https://ba.linkedin.com/in/harun-suljagic-477914201" target="_blank">HS</a>
